        <i class="bi bi-cpu fs-1 text-primary mb-3"></i>
        <h5>Innovative Research</h5>
        <p>Join pioneering teams in defense technology R&D.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
