        <h5>Secure Career</h5>
        <p>Benefit from stability and career growth in a national organization.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
        <i class="bi bi-globe fs-1 text-primary mb-3"></i>
        <h5>Global Impact</h5>
        <p>Be a part of India's strategic innovation landscape.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


